---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTABand from '@/components/CTABand.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Group Benefits & Savings Plans | Heidi Blondin Financial"
  description="Employer-sponsored group benefits that attract and retain great employees. Health, dental, life, disability, and group savings plans for Ontario businesses."
>

  <section class="bg-brand-plum py-20">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <p class="eyebrow-light mb-5">Insurance</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-display text-white text-balance" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Group Benefits & Savings Plans</h1>
      <p class="font-sans text-[18px] text-white/65 mt-5 leading-relaxed">
        A well-designed benefits package does more than keep people healthy — it signals that you value your team. We help Ontario employers build programs that attract talent and keep it.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-brand-plum mb-6" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Benefits that work for both sides</h2>
      <div class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>Group benefits are one of the most tax-efficient forms of employee compensation — the employer's premiums are generally a deductible business expense, and many benefits are received by employees tax-free. For small and medium-sized businesses in Ontario, a well-structured group plan levels the playing field with larger employers.</p>
        <p>We work with businesses of all sizes to design and administer group programs that fit their workforce, budget, and culture. Whether you're setting up a first plan or reviewing an existing arrangement, we'll walk you through every option.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        {[
          { title: 'Group health & dental', desc: 'Extended health, prescription drugs, dental, vision, and paramedical coverage. The cornerstone of most benefits packages.' },
          { title: 'Group life insurance', desc: 'Basic life coverage and accidental death & dismemberment — typically multiples of annual salary, easy to enrol, no medical required.' },
          { title: 'Short and long-term disability', desc: 'Income replacement coverage if an employee is unable to work due to illness or injury — protecting both the employee and the business.' },
          { title: 'Employee Assistance Program (EAP)', desc: 'Confidential mental health, counselling, and life advisory services that employees access on their own terms.' },
          { title: 'Group RRSP & DPSP', desc: 'Employer-matched savings plans that provide a powerful retention incentive and help employees build long-term financial security.' },
          { title: 'Group TFSA', desc: 'After-tax savings through a workplace program — flexible and valued by employees who may already be maximizing their RRSP.' },
        ].map(item => (
          <div class="bg-brand-tintPlum p-6">
            <h3 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-2">{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="font-sans text-[13px] text-brand-ink/65 leading-relaxed">{item.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 bg-brand-tintPlum p-5 border-l-2 border-brand-plum/30">
        <p class="font-sans text-xs text-brand-ink/55 leading-relaxed">Insurance products are offered through Heidi Blondin Financial / Qualified Financial Services. Mutual funds are offered through Investia Financial Services Inc. This article is for general information purposes only and does not constitute personalized financial or business advice. Please consult with a qualified advisor to determine what programs are appropriate for your business.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTABand heading="Build a benefits program your team will value" sub="Book a free consultation and we'll put together a proposal tailored to your business." />

</BaseLayout>
